{key}: {type(freon_data[key])}")\n \n # Extract compound information\n if \'compound\' in freon_data:\n compound = freon_data[\'compound\']\n molecular_weight = compound.get(\'molecular_weight\', 120.91) # g/mol\n print(f"\\nCompound: {compound.get(\'name\', \'Unknown\')}")\n print(f"Formula: {compound.get(\'formula\', \'Unknown\')}")\n print(f"Molecular Weight: {molecular_weight} g/mol")\n \n # Extract thermodynamic properties\n if \'thermodynamic_properties\' in freon_data:\n thermo_props = freon_data[\'thermodynamic_properties\']\n \n # Critical temperature\n Tc_data = thermo_props.get(\'critical_temperature\', {})\n Tc = Tc_data.get(\'average_value\', 385.0) # K\n print(f"\\nCritical Temperature: {Tc} K ({Tc - 273.15:.2f} ¬∞C)")\n \n # Critical pressure\n Pc_data = thermo_props.get(\'critical_pressure\', {})\n Pc = Pc_data.get(\'average_value\', 40.73) * 1e5 # Convert bar to Pa\n print(f"Critical Pressure: {Pc/1e5:.2f} bar ({Pc/1e6:.2f} MPa)")\n \n # Critical density\n rhoc_data = thermo_props.get(\'critical_density\', {})\n rhoc = rhoc_data.get(\'average_value\', 596.4) # kg/m¬≥\n print(f"Critical Density: {rhoc:.1f} kg/m¬≥")\nelse:\n print(f"Freon-12 properties file not found: {freon_props_file}")\n # Use default values\n molecular_weight = 120.91 # g/mol\n Tc = 385.0 # K\n Pc = 40.73e5 # Pa\n rhoc = 596.4 # kg/m¬≥\n\n# Load Marianas Trench environmental conditions\nmarianas_file = os.path.join(workspace_dir, \'marianas_trench_conditions.json\')\nif os.path.exists(marianas_file):\n print(f"\\nLoading Marianas Trench conditions from: {marianas_file}")\n \n # First inspect the structure\n with open(marianas_file, \'r\') as f:\n marianas_data = json.load(f)\n \n print("Marianas Trench data structure:")\n for key in marianas_data.keys():\n print(f" - {key}: {type(marianas_data[key])}")\n \n # Extract environmental conditions\n if \'established_measurements\' in marianas_data:\n measurements = marianas_data[\'established_measurements\']\n \n # Pressure at depth\n pressure_data = measurements.get(\'pressure_at_maximum_depth\', {})\n P_extreme = pressure_data.get(\'pressure_bar\', 1100) * 1e5 # Convert bar to Pa\n print(f"\\nPressure at Challenger Deep: {P_extreme/1e5:.0f} bar ({P_extreme/1e6:.0f} MPa)")\n \n # Temperature at depth\n temp_data = measurements.get(\'temperature_conditions\', {})\n T_extreme = temp_data.get(\'temperature_kelvin\', 275.15) # K\n print(f"Temperature at Challenger Deep: {T_extreme} K ({T_extreme - 273.15:.1f} ¬∞C)")\nelse:\n print(f"Marianas Trench conditions file not found: {marianas_file}")\n # Use default values\n P_extreme = 1100e5 # Pa (1100 bar)\n T_extreme = 275.15 # K (2¬∞C)\n\nprint(f"\\n=== STEP 2: PENG-ROBINSON EQUATION OF STATE IMPLEMENTATION ===")\nprint("Implementing Peng-Robinson EOS for high-pressure conditions...")\n\n# Constants\nR = 8.314 # Universal gas constant, J/(mol¬∑K)\nmass_freon = 0.312 # kg\nMW = molecular_weight / 1000 # Convert g/mol to kg/mol\nn_moles = mass_freon / MW # moles of Freon-12\n\nprint(f"\\nCalculation parameters:")\nprint(f"Mass of Freon-12: {mass_freon} kg")\nprint(f"Molecular weight: {molecular_weight} g/mol ({MW:.5f} kg/mol)")\nprint(f"Number of moles: {n_moles:.4f} mol")\nprint(f"Temperature: {T_extreme} K")\nprint(f"Pressure: {P_extreme/1e6:.0f} MPa")\n\n# Peng-Robinson equation parameters\ndef calculate_peng_robinson_parameters(T, Tc, Pc):\n """\n Calculate Peng-Robinson equation parameters\n """\n # Reduced temperature\n Tr = T / Tc\n \n # Peng-Robinson constants\n omega = 0.279 # Acentric factor for Freon-12 (CCl2F2)\n \n # Temperature-dependent parameter\n kappa = 0.37464 + 1.54226 * omega - 0.26992 * omega**2\n alpha = (1 + kappa * (1 - np.sqrt(Tr)))**2\n \n # Peng-Robinson parameters\n a = 0.45724 * (R * Tc)**2 / Pc * alpha\n b = 0.07780 * R * Tc / Pc\n \n return a, b, alpha, Tr\n\n# Calculate PR parameters\na, b, alpha, Tr = calculate_peng_robinson_parameters(T_extreme, Tc, Pc)\n\nprint(f"\\nPeng-Robinson parameters:")\nprint(f"Reduced temperature (Tr): {Tr:.4f}")\nprint(f"Parameter a: {a:.6e} Pa¬∑m‚Å∂¬∑mol‚Åª¬≤")\nprint(f"Parameter b: {b:.6e} m¬≥/mol")\nprint(f"Alpha: {alpha:.4f}")\n\n# Solve cubic equation for compressibility factor Z\ndef solve_peng_robinson_cubic(P, T, a, b):\n """\n Solve the Peng-Robinson cubic equation for compressibility factor Z\n """\n # Dimensionless parameters\n A = a * P / (R * T)**2\n B = b * P / (R * T)\n \n print(f"\\nDimensionless parameters:")\n print(f"A = {A:.6f}")\n print(f"B = {B:.6f}")\n \n # Cubic equation: Z¬≥ - (1-B)Z¬≤ + (A-3B¬≤-2B)Z - (AB-B¬≤-B¬≥) = 0\n coeffs = [\n 1, # Z¬≥ coefficient\n -(1 - B), # Z¬≤ coefficient\n A - 3*B**2 - 2*B, # Z coefficient\n -(A*B - B**2 - B**3) # constant term\n ]\n \n print(f"Cubic equation coefficients: {[f\'{c:.6f}\' for c in coeffs]}")\n \n # Solve cubic equation\n roots = np.roots(coeffs)\n \n print(f"\\nCubic equation roots:")\n real_roots = []\n for i, root in enumerate(roots):\n if np.isreal(root) and np.real(root) > 0:\n real_root = np.real(root)\n real_roots.append(real_root)\n print(f" Root {i+1}: {real_root:.6f} (real, positive)")\n else:\n print(f" Root {i+1}: {root} (complex or negative)")\n \n # For liquid phase at high pressure, choose the smallest positive real root\n if real_roots:\n Z = min(real_roots)\n print(f"\\nSelected compressibility factor Z: {Z:.6f} (liquid phase)")\n else:\n print("\\nWarning: No positive real roots found, using ideal gas approximation")\n Z = 1.0\n \n return Z, A, B\n\n# Calculate compressibility factor\nZ, A, B = solve_peng_robinson_cubic(P_extreme, T_extreme, a, b)\n\nprint(f"\\n=== STEP 3: VOLUME CALCULATION ===")\n\n# Calculate molar volume using Peng-Robinson EOS\n# PV = ZnRT, so V = ZnRT/P\nV_molar = Z * R * T_extreme / P_extreme # m¬≥/mol\nV_total = V_molar * n_moles # m¬≥\nV_total_ml = V_total * 1e6 # Convert m¬≥ to mL\n\nprint(f"\\nVolume calculations:")\nprint(f"Molar volume: {V_molar:.8e} m¬≥/mol")\nprint(f"Total volume: {V_total:.8e} m¬≥")\nprint(f"Total volume: {V_total_ml:.2f} mL")\n\n# Round to nearest integer as requested\nV_final_ml = round(V_total_ml)\n\nprint(f"\\n*** FINAL RESULT ***")\nprint(f"Volume of {mass_freon} kg Freon-12 at Marianas Trench conditions:")\nprint(f"Temperature: {T_extreme} K ({T_extreme - 273.15:.1f} ¬∞C)")\nprint(f"Pressure: {P_extreme/1e5:.0f} bar ({P_extreme/1e6:.0f} MPa)")\nprint(f"Volume: {V_final_ml} mL")\n\n# Verification calculations\nprint(f"\\n=== STEP 4: VERIFICATION AND ANALYSIS ===")\n\n# Calculate density\ndensity_calc = mass_freon / V_total # kg/m¬≥\nprint(f"\\nCalculated density: {density_calc:.1f} kg/m¬≥")\nprint(f"Critical density: {rhoc:.1f} kg/m¬≥")\nprint(f"Density ratio (œÅ/œÅc): {density_calc/rhoc:.3f}")\n\n# Compare with ideal gas (for reference)\nV_ideal = n_moles * R * T_extreme / P_extreme # m¬≥\nV_ideal_ml = V_ideal * 1e6 # mL\ncompression_factor = V_ideal_ml / V_total_ml\n\nprint(f"\\nComparison with ideal gas:")\nprint(f"Ideal gas volume: {V_ideal_ml:.2f} mL")\nprint(f"Peng-Robinson volume: {V_total_ml:.2f} mL")\nprint(f"Compression factor (V_ideal/V_real): {compression_factor:.2f}")\nprint(f"Volume reduction: {(1 -
